# Tech Stack

This file is the source of truth for the libraries, frameworks, and tools used in this project. **Keep it up to date — updating this file is the final step of every plan that introduces, removes, or changes a dependency or tool.**

---

- **Language / platform:** TypeScript, Obsidian API, CodeMirror 6 (Live Preview widgets)
- **Drawing / writing UI:** tldraw v2.x
- **Testing:** Jest (unit/integration), WebdriverIO + wdio-obsidian-service (e2e)
- **Build tooling:** esbuild (plugin bundling), npm scripts
- **Boox companion:** eInk Bridge Android app (`eink-bridge` repo) — loopback WebSocket on the same tablet
